            <paragraph>All comparison operators return booleans (<literal>==</literal>, <literal>&gt;</literal>, <literal>&lt;=</literal>, etc.). As such, it is not necessary to compare booleans themselves. You do not need to add <literal>== true</literal> or <literal>== false</literal>.</paragraph>
